:

*Slušao* je nastavnika iz matematike. (He listened to the math teacher.)
On je *slušao* svoj glas. (He was listening to his own voice.)
Ona je *slušala* glazbu. (She was listening to the music.)
Oni su *slušali* teoriju o rješavanju problema. (They were listening to the theory on problem solving.)
Deca su *slušala* bajke. (The children were listening to the fairy tales.)